# Making a simple calculator with all the operators (+,-,*,/,%)
Start

Ask the user to enter num1
Ask the user to enter num2
Ask the user to enter operator

Set Result to 0

If the operator = "+" then set Result to num1 + num2
Else
  If the operator = "-" then set Result to num1 - num2
  Else
    If the operator = "*" then set Result to num1 * num2
    Else
      If the operator = "/" then set Result to num1 / num2
      Else
        If the operator = "%" then set Result to (num1 / num2) * 100
        Else 
          Print "invalid operator"

Print Result

End
